Hello Lucy,

I have some questions regarding the challenge requirements.

1) Users can make reservations for more than 1 person or they can only make reservations for themselves?
    1.1) If users should be able to make reservations for more than 1 person, how is campsite organized? Is there some sort of boundary for each tent?
2) Should concurrent reservations be handled like flight reservations? When reserving a flight, users have some minutes to fill the forms and their seats (even if not marked yet) are pre-allocated during that time.
    2.1) In this case, what to do if a very large number of people are filling in at the same time? Anyone left out will be placed in a virtual queue? Or will these people find out if the reservation was successful only after filling out the form?
3) What is the expected number of unique website visitors in a single day?